.7349, 125.9892, 125.6049, 125.9027, 125.5621, 126.5806, 127.1027, 127.1053, 126.7487, 126.7561, 126.8848, 126.355, 126.4962, 124.9711, 126.5, 128.0972, 128.506, 129.2808, 130.5254, 128.5006, 127.4976, 128.3331, 128.9888, 128.9123, 127.5785, 130.0725, 130.0827, 132.8589, 131.8339, 131.827, 133.2806, 134.0843, 133.8384, 132.8295, 130.5182, 131.272, 130.3609, 131.6316, 129.8398, 131.4924, 130.9257, 131.3736, 131.9004, 132.1524, 130.959, 132.0715, 131.4724, 131.7849, 131.6029, 130.9583, 132.6055, 132.0817, 133.0223, 133.9889, 134.2973, 135.319, 134.073, 135.1346, 134.0676, 133.8663, 133.198, 132.642, 132.2321, 132.6895, 133.3356, 134.1544, 134.071, 134.7032, 134.9771, 135.4983, 135.5637, 135.1237, 136.3654, 135.2092, 134.1852, 133.1852, 131.2088, 130.5669, 130.5661, 129.7696, 129.9114, 130.751, 129.7295, 130.8454, 132.0489, 132.0326, 131.7322, 132.3435, 133.2011, 134.5321, 134.8833, 136.98, 138.361, 135.4741, 135.0462, 135.6551, 136.7351, 137.6887, 141.4223, 140.9303, 139.7195, 141.8151, 144.0955, 138.8611, 133.1093, 134.5572, 136.1795, 132.8465, 132.6485, 134.1491, 134.2463, 137.4122, 134.8547, 135.6572, 137.7599, 138.5199, 136.5537, 138.7614, 146.4864, 149.4825, 149.9295, 152.7616, 160.0286, 165.3709, 159.162, 163.4021, 164.4924, 163.3995, 164.6165, 164.4749, 165.8608, 164.1175, 167.179, 166.3061, 166.5736, 164.6311, 166.7764, 168.0771, 166.1695, 163.5775, 159.8846, 165.5557, 164.8215, 164.8785, 157.8272, 161.2169, 158.235, 158.558, 158.1283, 159.8338, 161.0942, 158.0002, 160.2925, 160.6451, 162.7461, 162.1333, 162.158, 163.5323, 164.2926, 165.2626, 164.9154, 164.3672, 162.4122, 162.498, 163.4752, 163.5458, 163.9674, 162.7413, 161.9269, 162.7267, 163.7623, 163.7808, 163.1469, 162.112, 162.1919, 162.0746, 161.5946], "summary_html": "<h1>AFH 改进因子 — 商品期货复现</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>报告核心思想是用处置效应 (Disposition Effect) 解释筹码因子有效性。原版 AFH (Actively and Flexibly Holding) 因子 = 主动小单买入筹码占比 = 过去 20 日(主买且金额&lt;5万元) 成交量之和 / 总成交量。报告在此基础上引入三个改进:</p>\n<p>1. <strong>AFH_Open</strong> — 用 <code>TradePrice/Open</code> 作为反向交易系数 α 2. <strong>AFH_Close</strong> — 用 <code>Close/TradePrice</code> 作为浮盈系数 α 3. <strong>AFH_Return</strong> — 用 <code>Close_T/TradePrice</code> (历史 20 日累计) 作为盈亏状态系数</p>\n<p><strong>AFH_Smart</strong> = <code>((AFH_Open + AFH_Close)/2 + AFH_Return) / 2</code></p>\n<p>原报告在中证 800/1000/2000 股票池 IC 均值 4.40%、多头超额 9.67%、信息比 2.02。</p>\n<p><strong>商品期货复现差异</strong>: A 股原始数据是逐笔成交, 商品期货只有分钟级 L2 (bvol/svol) + 分钟 K 线。映射方案: 1. <strong>小单 bar 标记</strong>: 每个 (sym, date) 内成交量 ≤ 30% 分位的 bar 标记为 <code>is_small=1</code> 2. <strong>主动买方向</strong>: L2 数据 <code>bvol &gt; svol</code> 标记 <code>is_buy=1</code> 3. <strong>筹码量 <code>vol_AFH</code></strong>: <code>volume * is_small * is_buy</code> 4. <strong>TradePrice</strong>: <code>(high+low+close)/3</code> (单 bar 典型价) 5. <strong>AFH_Return 数学拆解</strong>: <code>Close_T*Σ(vol_AFH/trade_price) - Σ(vol_AFH)</code> (避免 N×T 矩阵)</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.4%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>7.9%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-20.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3434</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.97</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.48 / 1.34</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.74</td><td>1.04</td><td>0.13</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.06</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.97</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.37</span></td><td>1.44</td><td>0.32</td><td>0.74</td><td>1.13</td><td>1.1</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.04</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 15 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 15 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3436</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>70.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">AFH = \\frac{\\sum_{t=T-20}^{T}\\sum_{i\\in\\text{small,buy}}\\text{vol}_i}{\\sum_{t=T-20}^{T}\\text{Volume}_t}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">AFH\\_Open = \\frac{\\sum_{i}\\alpha_{i,\\text{open}} \\cdot \\text{vol}_i}{\\sum \\text{Volume}}, \\quad \\alpha_{i,\\text{open}} = \\frac{\\text{TradePrice}_i}{\\text{Open}_t} - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">AFH\\_Close = \\frac{\\sum \\alpha_{i,\\text{close}} \\cdot \\text{vol}_i}{\\sum \\text{Volume}}, \\quad \\alpha_{i,\\text{close}} = \\frac{\\text{Close}_t}{\\text{TradePrice}_i} - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">AFH\\_Return_T = \\frac{\\text{Close}_T \\cdot \\sum (\\text{vol}_i/\\text{TradePrice}_i) - \\sum \\text{vol}_i}{\\sum \\text{Volume}}</div>\n<p>仓位生成: <code>cr_rank → rank_to_continuous(scale=2) → vol_target_scale(15%, 60d) → rebalance_hold(10d)</code></p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.18)</strong>: 实现 AFH_base + 4 个改进因子, 5 因子 × 双向 × 3 normalization = 30 变体. 截面 IC 0.0055, 时序 IC -0.003, 几乎无信号. 最优 AFH_base_pos_cs Sharpe 0.18. 诊断显示 V/I/FG 拖累.</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.02 — dirfix)</strong>: 加入多窗口 (20/40/60)、双 hold (10/20)、<strong>per-symbol direction fix</strong> (在 2016-2020 段算 sym×factor 与未来 5 日收益的 IC, sign 决定方向). 这个 dirfix 把方向不固定问题解决了, best Sharpe 暴涨到 1.02. 但有 in-sample 污染.</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 0.57 — honest)</strong>: 用 walk-forward 滚动 IC sign 替换 in-sample sign (每日只用过去 252 日 IC, 无前视). best Sharpe 0.57. Pipeline 触发 fallback (gap&gt;0.1), 回退到 R2 spec_best.</p>\n<p><strong>R4-R5</strong>: 重复 walk-forward 尝试一致 (~0.57). Pipeline 始终回退到 R2 dirfix.</p>\n<p><strong>关键发现</strong>: AFH 因子在商品期货截面 IC 较弱 (0.007), 方向不稳定 (~半数品种反向). 引入 per-sym direction 是必要的, walk-forward 后 Sharpe 仅 0.57. <strong>R2 报告的 1.02 含 in-sample sign-fit 污染</strong>.</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据</strong>: 日频量价 + 分钟 K 线 + 分钟 L2 (bvol/svol). L2 数据 2015+ 覆盖</li>\n<li><strong>品种</strong>: 商品期货全品种 (有 L2 数据的 45-58 个)</li>\n<li><strong>频率</strong>: 日频持仓, 10 天 rebalance</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 默认 10 日</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>已知局限</h3>\n<p>1. <strong>In-sample sign-fit 污染 (致命)</strong>: 最优变体 dirfix 在 2016-2020 段用了 in-sample 学到的 sign. 真实 OOS Sharpe 应参考 second_half=1.31 或 honest walk-forward 0.57. <strong>入实盘前必须改为完全 walk-forward direction</strong> 2. <strong>数据映射粗糙</strong>: A 股逐笔的 &lt;5万元小单 商品期货只能用 \"成交量底部 30% 分位 bar\" 代替, 信号衰减 3. <strong>换手率极高 (1.22 日均)</strong>: 总手续费 111% 严重侵蚀; 实盘成本敏感 4. <strong>方向不稳</strong>: V/UR/OI/AG 表现差, I/J/SM/JM 黑色系优秀 5. <strong>OOS 表现</strong>: 2024-2025 Sharpe 2.29/2.42 较好</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>SMALL_PCT</code></td><td>0.3</td><td>0.2-0.5</td><td>小单 bar 阈值 (当日成交量分位)</td></tr><tr><td><code>LB_LIST</code></td><td>[20, 40, 60]</td><td>—</td><td>滚动窗口 (报告原始 20 日)</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td>10, 20</td><td>5-40</td><td>仓位持有期</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_TARGET</code></td><td>0.15</td><td>—</td><td>波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_WINDOW</code></td><td>60</td><td>—</td><td>vol_target lookback</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9858</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 72.32s</li>\n</ul>"}